          "text": "set %complaint% = \u0022Compiler returned missing-actions for step %step.Index% (text: \u0027%step.Text%\u0027). Current action set is insufficient: %planStep.actions%. Reason: %!error.Message%. Return a corrected action set for step %step.Index% only.\u0022, type=string",
